{"tid":1513660,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"如果10月1號前執好、練好首《願榮光歸香港》，將會大大打擊中共面子","createTime":"2019-08-28T12:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:50:39.000Z","uid":309398,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2fcd489915d1d869f977697ed34289cd2cdd6dc8","tid":1513660,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"唔想搶左光環，所以請入link聽番首歌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507129</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我一聽首歌就已經有左<span style=\"color: red;\">歸屬感</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且首歌幾振奮人心，佢嘅心血唔應該咁快沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時我又想像緊<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果101前可以執好首歌</span></span>，全部人都練好佢，再響集會嗰陣齊唱，係會幾咁壯觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，希望大家可以幫佢整好首歌，而我亦唔想騎劫左佢原本作曲嘅目的，只係認為101一齊唱會好有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一齊比吓意見"},{"pid":"21f4794a023e2b2536b170944dc34301b70c0156","tid":1513660,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6e98a2b974b850ab6a59a90143593a3f18ff86","tid":1513660,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"呢個舊post<br />\n有新post更新左歌詞"},{"pid":"3a7e21e6bef0ac0e501f1acdbd9ff4e0db835f65","tid":1513660,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:12:04.000Z","msg":"新post<br />\n抗爭者軍歌《願榮光歸香港》新版詞！！ 招唱/管樂/軍樂隊！！！重開幫推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512905</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"305ff5584572fe547a390636a5a7d751667dc3a5","tid":15136